content: Singaporean politician **Jean See Jinli** is a Singaporean who served as a [Nominated Member of Parliament](/wiki/Nominated_Member_of_Parliament) commencing 2023. She was the director of [National Trades Union Congress](/wiki/National_Trades_Union_Congress) (NTUC) Freelancers and Self-Employed (U FSE) Unit. She was awarded with the Public Service Medal (COVID-19). This article about a politician from Singapore is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it. - v - t - e
